Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:56.77,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}木々をゆらしてゆく
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:02.78,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}あたたかい風に
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:09.72,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}少しまだ戸惑う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:16.00,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}臆病なわたし
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.70,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}もっと近づけたら
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.76,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}きみに屆くのかな
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.33,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}素直になれなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:34.24,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}からまわる 心の聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:43.42,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}いま気付いた この胸の奧で
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:50.28,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}芽生えだした蕾がある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:57.12,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}ひとみ そらさないで
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:03.75,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}見つけたい 芽生えた蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:13.93,OPJP,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}歩いてく きみへ向かう道
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:56.77,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}樹林搖擺不停
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.85,0:05:02.78,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}正因暖風吹拂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.40,0:05:09.72,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}尚有些許困惑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:16.00,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}如此膽小的我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.29,0:05:19.70,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}如果再接近你一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.70,0:05:22.76,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}真的能傳達給你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.76,0:05:26.33,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}無法變得率直
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.33,0:05:34.24,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}徘徊不決的心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.11,0:05:43.42,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}如今才注意到 胸口深處
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.42,0:05:50.28,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}那漸漸萌芽的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:57.12,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}不要移開視線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.20,0:06:03.75,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}想去尋找 那萌發的花蕾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:13.93,OPCH,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\c&H1E71AC&\an7\blur2}我將踏上 去往你身邊的路
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}＝＝＝
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.29,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}母親大人 姐姐大人 我是小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我要去白夜的老家了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我想會在晚上前回家
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.06,0:07:00.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然聽媽媽的話回來是對的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可以摘到這麼多春天的野菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼多的話小紅也會開心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.86,0:07:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為她說過想嚐嚐我們這裡的野菜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.20,0:07:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 開始下雪了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.92,0:07:23.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我聽到小紅的聲音了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.59,0:07:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不會吧 小紅應該在家裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.72,0:07:39.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 真白
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.42,0:08:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好冷 我會怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.26,0:08:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道是從冬眠中醒來的熊之類的？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.22,0:08:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜！
