Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.19,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:28.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅？！你在這裡做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:30.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.23,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個突然不見就追過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:36.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們只是來摘野菜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.70,0:08:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}順便把我們的成績單拿給媽媽看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.20,0:08:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成績單？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.50,0:08:44.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}成績單果然還是要給家長過目的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是 你們為什麼還把房間打掃的那麼乾淨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.21,0:08:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}衣服和課本也都不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}衣服是因為要換春裝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}教科書是因為升到二年級用不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.01,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}想放回家裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.14,0:09:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}話說 白夜不是發給小紅郵件了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了 郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.15,0:09:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一般這種時候都會在後面寫上「去去就來」「很快就回來」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}難道你沒看到我發的郵件嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.32,0:09:19.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}郵件？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.62,0:09:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這附近沒有信號
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.33,0:09:27.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.54,0:09:29.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}別讓我這麼擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}急死我了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.92,0:09:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你那麼擔心我們嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.05,0:09:38.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.55,0:09:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不只是我 姐姐大人和母親大人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.81,0:09:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}咦 一放鬆怎麼突然…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}小紅？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.69,0:09:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 小紅！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.29,0:10:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦才好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.66,0:10:09.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}為什麼偏偏遇到暴風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:12.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}雖然這裡可以避風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.54,0:10:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但如果不趕快讓小紅回家休息的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.26,0:10:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 你能抱著小紅跑嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.47,0:10:22.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能 不過這麼大的風雪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.22,0:10:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅會凍僵的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.14,0:10:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我去叫人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白在這裡陪她
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我知道了 你快點回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撐住啊 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.32,0:10:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜很快就會回來接你的
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.63,0:11:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 糟了 這樣下去火堆會滅掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.85,0:11:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}現在的話應該可以去撿些柴火
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我很快就回來 等我一下
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.04,0:11:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我們走了哦 小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.75,0:11:37.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要乖乖待在家裡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.01,0:11:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好的 慢走
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.68,0:11:46.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家 都漸漸離開了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我不像母親大人和姐姐大人學習那麼優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.35,0:11:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}也不擅長運動
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.32,0:11:58.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只會做家務
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:01.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果秘密被別人知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.03,0:12:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就不能留在這裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}傷疤的事 不想讓你知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.67,0:12:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}連白夜和真白都要離開了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.42,0:12:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜 真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.64,0:12:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}去哪裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.72,0:12:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又要丟下我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.53,0:12:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉 撿樹枝花了一些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.45,0:12:51.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.83,0:12:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.33,0:12:56.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.75,0:13:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不見了 在我去找薪柴的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}趕快找找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.76,0:13:06.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}發著燒應該走不了太遠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.22,0:13:08.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好 分頭找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.01,0:13:11.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要擔心 真白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.43,0:13:14.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們這麼多人肯定馬上就能找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.29,0:13:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.79,0:13:42.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}怎麼辦 要是小紅出了什麼事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}都是我的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.26,0:13:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是真白的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如果我能再早一點趕回來的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你們兩個都冷靜一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.89,0:13:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}找找看有沒有腳印之類的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.10,0:14:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是白夜的外套
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅一定就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.32,0:14:12.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我…什麼時候到這裡來了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.86,0:14:45.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:49.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這次…趕上了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖暖的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}身體好點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:05.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}已經沒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.50,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}暖和起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.46,0:15:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.01,0:15:09.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.22,0:15:12.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}正在附近找你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是嗎 是我讓你們擔心了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那時也像現在這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我動不了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是白夜陪在我身邊
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.01,0:15:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是說你的傷痕不是因為我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.30,0:15:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}一開始就不用隱瞞了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.10,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是被你知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.14,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺你會很介意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}當然了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.52,0:16:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}很介意 很吃驚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:07.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}感覺很抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是這麼重要的事情還是希望你別隱瞞我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.24,0:16:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.12,0:16:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}根本就不用隱瞞的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.70,0:16:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們不是未婚夫妻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.38,0:16:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.51,0:16:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}以後不會了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.59,0:16:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}再也不會隱瞞你了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}知道就好
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.10,0:16:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.90,0:16:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.48,0:16:49.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}右眼看不見嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}能看到光線
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.78,0:16:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我早就習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是小紅的錯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.00,0:17:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}白夜和小紅在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅 白夜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.84,0:17:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰家的媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}啊 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.01,0:17:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}太好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.80,0:17:21.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們馬上去你那邊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.56,0:17:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這下放心了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.69,0:17:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.98,0:17:31.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.19,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}紅緒
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.32,0:17:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真由良家公司的直升機啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.78,0:17:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為小紅你失蹤了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.20,0:17:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以我告訴了小紅的媽媽和紅緒醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.45,0:17:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我自己都忘記了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.08,0:17:46.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅和真白碳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.87,0:17:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒受傷吧 冷不冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.75,0:17:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}讓我們互相溫暖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.67,0:17:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}把責任都給冬天吧！
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.14,0:18:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那麼 你們兩個人在一起的時候有沒有發生什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什什什什…什麼事都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.77,0:18:09.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼事…都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.02,0:18:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.56,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}可是兩個人在雪山上獨處
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好浪漫的說
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.44,0:18:18.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這樣一來兩個人之間的感情不就一下子加深了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.78,0:18:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\pos(640,710)}那個表情算什麼啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\move(640,670,640,710,402,777)}什麼什麼表情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.33,0:18:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這麼說人家的哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}姐姐大人你冷靜一點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬你的聲音也很大的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們走囉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}慢走 注意安全哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.02,0:18:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}升到2年級還是跟真由良在一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.48,0:18:54.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是的呢 白夜同學和真白醬也在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.57,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯 嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.57,0:19:03.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}大家都在一個班
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.37,0:19:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是不是你又使用能力了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.33,0:19:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 你說啥呢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.79,0:19:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下來 UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.33,0:19:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用UMA來贏得獨家新聞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.12,0:19:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\shad0\fs20\pos(606,443)}謝禮是摩克拉姆貝貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}木葉要是找到了未確認生物的話要告訴我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:20.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小紅醬和真白醬
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.05,0:19:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到這張海報了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.68,0:19:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}摩克拉姆貝貝
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我現在主要以這個方向取材
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.68,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}有任何發現要聯絡我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仁子醬看到的不會是你吧 小不點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.44,0:19:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不是 倒不如說是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.69,0:19:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}你朋友要找的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.86,0:19:40.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我又不是UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.28,0:19:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是很出色又有歷史的一族呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.16,0:19:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那我也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.70,0:19:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}三峰家是歷史悠久的一族
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.91,0:19:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}才不是UMA呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.62,0:19:50.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}UMA UMA 呀 UMA
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.87,0:19:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好大的UMA味
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.21,0:19:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}喂 討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}說別人是UMA的才是UMA呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.75,0:19:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}先說UMA的是你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.05,0:20:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是你先說的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.38,0:20:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新聞部好像是在收集UMA的情報呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.80,0:20:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好像是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.01,0:20:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明明有比UMA好的特集呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.52,0:20:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.06,0:20:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.85,0:20:13.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}妹妹特集
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.02,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是什麼校內報刊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:16.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}特集 妹妹游泳大會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.98,0:20:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}參賽隊是 親生妹妹和義理妹妹隊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}{\an8}這個故事好像挺長…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.86,0:20:25.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}新學期到了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.12,0:20:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}春天將至
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.99,0:20:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是還是一如既往的熱鬧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好可…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:38.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}接下來我們會如何進展現在還不知道
Comment: 0,0:00:00.85,0:00:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.84,0:20:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}但是暫時還是會繼續這樣的生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.14,0:20:52.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這是在我家附近採的蘑菇和野菜
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.85,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}哇 謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.28,0:21:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我們回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因為要到附近辦事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.99,0:21:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就打算順便送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}是辦什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.62,0:21:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}這裡有好多美味的食品店
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.08,0:21:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}要是把末續也叫來就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}那倒不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.88,0:21:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}我跟她可是敵對關係呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}又說這種話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.18,0:21:28.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}小魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.60,0:21:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}用掃帚飛到天上去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}看到好東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.06,0:21:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}騎著掃帚飛天？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.77,0:21:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}真白醬 到底什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.02,0:21:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}什麼都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.57,0:21:47.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}好吃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.28,0:21:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只要是小紅做的 什麼都好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.49,0:21:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}所以啊…不要輕易就這麼說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.55,0:22:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}嘛 算了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.48,0:00:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
